snippet.title: VIDEOVERSE - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A short teaser for my next game, VIDEOVERSE, which is coming soon to PC, Mac and Linux!

Take a trip back to the days of the early internet and fan forums, when the video game console "Kinmoku Shark" and its online social network "Videoverse" were still popular...

Wishlist/ Follow on:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2079180/VIDEOVERSE
itch.io - https://kinmoku.itch.io/videoverse

More information and press-kit available at: http://gamesbykinmoku.epizy.com/videoverse/
